data.title: Zoology Chapter 4
data.meta_description: Zoology Chapter 4 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides an overview of the Zoology textbook for Class XI. It includes chapters on the Animal Kingdom, general features of animals such as their levels of organization, body plans, symmetry, germ layers, body cavity, segmentation, and notochord. It also provides a basic classification of the Kingdom Animalia and details on the phylum Porifera, commonly known as sponges. The document serves as an introduction to zoology and the classification and characteristics of different animal groups.
